form_title.ms_form_title_llm_v1: Quality Assurance Checklist, Task B - CONTINUED CASES CHECKLIST

full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/13/2023 A 10 417 818 Quality Assurance Checklist Office Code Los Task B - CONTINUED CASES CHECK LIST Yes No N/A Comments 1. Was the N-400 Processing Worksheet completed to show whether applicant appeared for interview? 2. Is reason for continuation clearly indicated on the N-400 Processing Worksheet? 3. If reexamination for Sec 312 eligibility, does the N-400 Processing Worksheet indicate that the case has been rescheduled within 90 days after initial interview? 4. If claiming a disability exception, and the N-648 submitted was not acceptable, does N-400 Processing Worksheet indicate that a supplemental disability determination was requested? 5. Was application signed by applicant at time of interview? No English 6. Was application signed by officer at time of interview? 7. Were the N-400 questions which were asked by DAO and answered during the interview checked off or circled in red ink? 8a. Were all annotations/changes made by DAO noted on the N-400 attestation in red ink, 8b. and numbered in red ink? 9. Are all signatures correct? 10. Has any necessary additional documentation been requested on an N-14? 11. If so, does the N-14 give the applicant a due date to submit the additional documentation? 12. Did the N-400 Processing Worksheet contain the results of over 15 the FBI fingerprint check prior to the time of interview? / Rev.5/23/97 Attachment 13 fletcolon 7-20-98 Reviewer's Signature (Date) USE SEPARATE SHEET FOR ADDITIONAL COMMENTS (Include on separate sheet: Task B (con't), A#, Reviewer's signature, and date)
